Vxglue

Vxglue is a set of routines that integrate with
C/C++ language VXML implementations.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

Look at voiceglue.org for further information.

